Blackline accounting software by GoPlan is a scalable platform appropriate for companies in various industries. Healthcare companies, higher education, nonprofit organizations, pharmaceutical companies, maintenance and field service providers, insurance agencies, distributors, manufacturers, software companies, and businesses in numerous other industries can customize the program to accommodate their needs.
Key features of Blackline include budgeting and forecasting and financial reporting.  Companies can manage separate business lines from user licenses. Budgets can be set for both internal and external compliance. Reporting is available for companies to retroactively analyze trends and expenditures. Forecasting is an essential tool available in order to plan revenue streams and predict spend agility.
The system is entirely web-based and can be accessed via mobile devices as well as desktops.



 


















 








