Blackline Manufacturing
For screen printers, the messy process of reclaiming screens, ink removal and waste management can be frustrating and arduous, especially if you’re using the wrong equipment. Blackline Manufacturing exists to help ease your clean room workflow and get you back on the press.
Blackline Mfg. features a full line of washout sinks, filtration systems and ink cleaning stations to fit your screen print shop needs – all of which are designed to be used with environmentally friendly biodegradable chemicals. Our products are built of tough, durable, welded polypropylene plastic, and feature high-end components that are built to last.
 

